WEBVTT

00:00:08.863 --> 00:00:17.162 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When Jesus was on earth,
he had some very special friends.

00:00:17.162 --> 00:00:24.420 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They were called apostles,
and there were twelve of them.

00:00:24.420 --> 00:00:33.053 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They were there when Jesus healed the sick,
the blind, the deaf, and lame.

00:00:33.053 --> 00:00:40.394 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now let’s try to remember
all twelve of them by name.

00:00:40.394 --> 00:00:56.452 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There was Peter, James, John, Andrew,
Philip, Thomas, Judas, Matthew,

00:00:56.452 --> 00:01:08.339 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
The other James, Simon, and Thaddaeus,
And don’t forget Bartholomew.

00:01:08.339 --> 00:01:17.264 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They were men who spent their time
with Jesus preaching.

00:01:17.264 --> 00:01:24.980 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They were working hard
to listen to Jesus’ teachings.

00:01:24.980 --> 00:01:33.530 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But one of them disobeyed;
he did not keep his faith.

00:01:33.530 --> 00:01:41.246 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now let’s try to remember
all twelve of them by name.

00:01:41.246 --> 00:01:56.971 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There was Peter, James, John, Andrew,
Philip, Thomas, Judas, Matthew,

00:01:56.971 --> 00:02:11.360 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
The other James, Simon, and Thaddaeus,
And don’t forget Bartholomew.

